                            <comment id="12782284" author="apurtell" created="Wed, 25 Nov 2009 02:26:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Committed to trunk and 0.20 branch. Changes:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add master and region server opts independently to hbase-env.sh
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Modify GC flags to Ryan&apos;s recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Enable GC logging&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Split Hadoop config into core, hdfs, and mapred-site.xml&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Configure mapreduce and start jobtracker and tasktrackers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Silence sysctl warning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Add hbase jars and conf dir to Hadoop classpath&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Use port 8020 for HDFS and 8021 for jobtracker&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

</comment>
